title: New: Katéa – That Ain’t Love
content:
Listing Tove Lo, Adele and Lana Del Rey amongst her influences, it’s clear that Helsinki newcomer Katéa is setting the bar high, and her debut single, That Ain’t Love, certainly strives to reach those lofty heights.

A booming, Florence & The Machine-esque number, her vocal takes centre stage, building the track around a chorus of colossal proportions. Check it out below.
